I'm troubled.

36:07.249 --> 36:09.542
Now, Project Icarus is gone.

36:09.543 --> 36:11.169
Project Incubus is dying.

36:11.170 --> 36:13.129
You got three normal civilians

36:13.130 --> 36:14.714
that have thus far gone uncaptured.

36:14.715 --> 36:18.634
You are living in a world
full of empty rooms that need filling.

36:18.635 --> 36:19.594
Someone up high somewhere,

36:19.595 --> 36:21.429
they're going to see
this is out of control,

36:21.430 --> 36:23.848
and you are going
to be embarrassed,

36:23.849 --> 36:26.767
and you are going
to be replaced,

36:26.768 --> 36:29.646
but I can give you a win.

36:36.111 --> 36:38.446
A rash of assaults
and sightings.

36:38.447 --> 36:41.157
Incubus Number Four and the Brotzman girl,

36:41.158 --> 36:42.742
the one who embarrassed you.

36:42.743 --> 36:44.327
I can get them.

36:44.328 --> 36:46.787
You've just had this information?

36:46.788 --> 36:48.873
So have you,
if you read the reports,

36:48.874 --> 36:50.666
but you don't, do you?

36:50.667 --> 36:53.127
I like that in a leader.

36:53.128 --> 36:55.672
I like a guy
who doesn't sweat the details.

36:58.133 --> 37:01.302
